data: {"type":"text_delta","text":"Saturday"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" morning is wide open before the 3:45 PM match — you've got a good"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" stretch of free time, which is actually a gift with a"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" tournament day. A few directions worth thinking about:\n\n**Ease"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" into the day near the bungalow.** If the beach is accessible"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" from 41 Lower Boulevard, a low-key morning walk along the water could be"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" perfect — Rafa gets to run around, you"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" get golden-hour light for photos, and nobody burns energy they"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" need for the afternoon. New London has some nice coastal texture if"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" you're into that kind of thing.\n\n**Explore Mystic or the surrounding area.** Mystic is"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" a short hop from New London and has a really photogenic downtown"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" — drawbridge, seaport, good breakfast spots."}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" Rafa tends to do well with places that have things to *"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":"look* at and touch, and Mystic Seaport has hands"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":"-on ship stuff he'd probably love. Worth checking app"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" hours before you go, but it could be a solid 2"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":"–3 hour morning without rushing back.\n\n**Mohegan Sun itself has"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" a lot inside it.** If you want to minimize driving and just land"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" near the venue early, the resort has restaurants, an arcade"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":", and enough to keep kids occupied. Lower-stimulation than"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" a full excursion, but super convenient — and you'd"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" be parked and calm before the match.\n\nThe one thing I'd flag: Aurelia will probably"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" want a warmup window before the 3:45 match, so"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" mentally I'd plan to wrap any outing"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" by around 2:30 at the latest to give her that buffer"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" without rushing.\n\nWhat sounds most like your family's Saturday"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" vibe — adventurous morning out, or relaxed and close"}

data: {"type":"text_delta","text":" to home?"}

